fields.physical_description: Design: chrowmolithographs, on the reverse sides printed in pale green to show british flags and emblems of the monarchy; sets consist of three parts, head, middle and feet of a doll-like figure dress in various costumes including national costumes - each set is named.
fields.title: Golly Misfitz

Equipment required: 48 cards arranged in 16 sets of three; each set being the head, middle and feet of a figure - each set of three is named
